{"tid":417094,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位中學或以下嘅少年講下你地個Account係點得嚟","createTime":"2017-09-28T10:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T15:27:31.000Z","uid":1393,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"30354a577af3948b060dc622b1324d761c98b9e5","tid":417094,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:45:54.000Z","msg":"家人登記嘅ISP Email?<br />\n<br />\n中學email可以申請?<br />\n<br />\n定其他方法?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我個人唔抗拒有年輕會員。始終一個論壇必定需要新血。如果唔係過多十幾廿年，連登變咗一個只係一班中坑打飛機嘅地方。<br />\n<br />\n但希望你學下咩叫理性思考，相比起以前高登，連登好容易出現爆like嘅現象。通常前100個like / dislike 就主導哂之後嘅風向。呢點令打手做野變得好容易。<br />\n<br />\n記住呢度唔係facebook，你持相反意見冇人知你係乜水。"},{"pid":"63215302adead2e28efe7ac5fc940def73c55233","tid":417094,"uid":20448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"到自己出黎做野join 上網plan 先開始有email 申請Account<br />\n<br />\n利申：上左五年都有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f85e7e7ad670e77e1247ce1a7d67c1987296976","tid":417094,"uid":31824,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"少年，你太年輕了。你以為連登真的有那麼多人回覆你的帖子？其實都是我一個人回的，不然我換個ID發同樣的話給你看。"},{"pid":"c399715124e393a9e35ca101490c70d1e6b6d4f8","tid":417094,"uid":51269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:58:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到自己出黎做野join 上網plan 先開始有email 申請Account<br />\n<br />\n利申：上左五年都有了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來連登有五年架啦 唔通我穿越左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老味 人地問連登ac 你就答高登+連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b76e92d257766f277a6c2c9a05ffb8657d7433","tid":417094,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"邀請碼，ISP比家姐用左"},{"pid":"6990109a4796d289753b5037ca4fba4c38b98735","tid":417094,"uid":1393,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"